149
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,480
You hit me.

150
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,340
Don't touch me.

151
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,120
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

152
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,050
