231
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,370
Don't be afraid.

232
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:53,320
Tian Liang committed many crimes.

233
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,380
He deserved to die.

234
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:56,730
