237
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:04,640
Qiandabaolv City.

238
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:08,650
Mr. Zhao.

239
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:09,920
Captain Shen,

240
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:10,780
Captain Jiang.

241
