291
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:21,160
Panpan.

292
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:28,980
Panpan.

293
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:32,120
What did the police officers ask you just now?

294
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,520
They showed me a photo

295
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,820
and asked who the person in it was.

296
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,320
A photo?

297
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:43,720
Zhao.

298
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,580
Captain Jiang.

299
00:13:44,640 --> 00:13:45,370
How did it go?

300
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,280
We have a motive,

301
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,560
but no evidence right now.

302
00:13:48,560 --> 00:13:49,720
We'll figure it out eventually.

303
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,200
Master.

304
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:51,680
Captain Shen.

305
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:54,000
Master, the call records you asked me to check,

306
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:54,800
I've got them.

307
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:02,690
Where are you going?

308
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:03,680
Shen Feng,

309
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,170
give it to me.

310
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:09,600
Yu Na and Xia Lin.

311
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:12,720
Liuzi, have some water.

312
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,440
Okay, thank you.

313
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,520
How have you been lately?

314
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:14,980
Not bad.

315
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:15,920
Same as usual.

316
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:16,880
I need a favor.

317
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:18,760
Don't say that. Just tell me.

318
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:20,160
Help me find Yu Na.

319
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,760
I have something to ask her.

320
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:22,360
Yu Na.

321
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:24,880
Manager Yu should be out meeting clients.

322
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:25,920
Is something wrong, brother?

323
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:27,480
Just someone related to a case.

324
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,720
A routine inquiry.

325
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:31,090
This woman is quite something.

326
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:33,200
Last year, I don't know what method she used

327
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:34,080
to get a piece of land.

328
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:36,540
The land right next to Wutong Neighborhood.

329
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:37,440
And then?

330
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:39,360
She was suddenly promoted to vice president

331
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:41,480
and put in charge of the company's finances.

332
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,880
That's a fast promotion.

333
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:43,960
Yeah.

334
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,800
Yu Na is very capable.

335
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,960
Otherwise, Mr. Ye wouldn't value her so much.

336
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,840
In our company,

337
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,410
as long as you work hard,

338
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:52,520
the boss will never treat you poorly.

339
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,840
There are still such good bosses nowadays?

340
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,100
Yes, it's rare, right?

341
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:55,920
With such a good boss,

342
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:58,180
brother, why haven't you been promoted?

343
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:01,800
Could there be something going on between Yu Na and Mr. Ye?

344
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,320
That shouldn't be possible.

345
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:06,480
Mr. Ye is famously devoted to his wife.

346
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:07,320
In the company,

347
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,650
from the sales, budget,

348
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:10,760
to the finance departments,

349
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:12,360
there are over 30 female employees,

350
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,600
and every one of them is beautiful.

351
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:14,560
But our Mr. Ye

352
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:15,600
doesn't even glance at them.

353
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,280
He only focuses on his work.

354
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:18,640
A true gentleman.

355
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:22,080
Liuzi, what we talked about today,

356
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,000
you know the rules.

357
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:23,730
Understood.

358
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:24,730
Keep it a secret.

359
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:27,520
Invite Yu Na for coffee on my behalf at 4:00.

360
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:28,440
Okay, no problem.

361
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,040
Go get back to work.

362
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:29,800
All right, contact me anytime if you need something.

363
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:30,600
Give me a call.

364
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,920
4:00 p.m. at the cafe.

365
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:44,800
Thank you.

366
00:15:46,040 --> 00:15:46,700
Manager Yu.

367
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:47,720
I'm very sorry

368
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,160
for taking the liberty of having Liuzi ask you out.

369
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,320
Thank you for your cooperation.

370
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:50,920
It's fine.

371
00:15:51,800 --> 00:15:52,560
Hello, Manager Yu.

372
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:53,360
I am Jiang Mei.

373
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:54,080
Hello.

374
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:55,520
We came here today

375
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:56,360
just to ask you

376
00:15:56,520 --> 00:15:57,880
how you met Tian Liang.

377
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,260
Tian Liang?

378
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,690
He is a trainer at my gym.

379
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:03,570
Have you seen him recently?

380
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,320
No.

381
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,370
He's missing. Did you know?

382
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,640
I know now.

383
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,560
On the night of July 25,

384
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:12,890
you two had a phone call.

385
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,440
It was around 10:43 PM,

386
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:16,080
lasting for a minute and a half.

387
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:17,410
What did you talk about?

388
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:23,880
That day, I think I was helping a friend

389
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,680
ask about signing up for his class.

390
00:16:25,680 --> 00:16:27,080
You remember so clearly.

391
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:28,320
Of course.

392
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:30,320
It's not someone I contact often.

393
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:32,400
Do you meet Tian Liang often?

394
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:45,080
Ms. Yu.

395
00:16:58,640 --> 00:17:00,770
Keep your dirty thoughts to yourself.

396
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:06,800
Ms. Yu,

397
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,640
you are so beautiful.

398
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,730
Why are you so hung up on one guy?

399
00:17:12,319 --> 00:17:13,650
Mind your own business.

400
00:17:15,359 --> 00:17:15,800
Fine.

401
00:17:18,359 --> 00:17:20,160
He has probably seen the photos.

402
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:21,920
As for what happens next,

403
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:23,400
I can't guarantee it.

404
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:26,520
Get out.

405
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:29,320
Not often.
